title: Abby and Brittany (2012)
description: Abby & Brittany was an American reality show on TLC starring 22-year-old conjoined twins Abigail and Brittany Hensel that premiered on August 28, 2012. The show features their graduation from Bethel University, subsequent job search, and their travels in Europe. It was broadcast on BBC Three in the UK in April and May 2013, as three 60-minute episodes
